title: Google\Cloud\Scheduler\V1beta1\PubsubTarget
name: PubsubTarget
description:
Pub/Sub target. The job will be delivered by publishing a message to the given Pub/Sub topic.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.scheduler.v1beta1.PubsubTarget

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.topic_name
params.description: Required. The name of the Cloud Pub/Sub topic to which messages will be published when a job is delivered. The topic name must be in the same format as required by PubSub's PublishRequest.name, for example projects/PROJECT_ID/topics/TOPIC_ID. The topic must be in the same project as the Cloud Scheduler job.
